<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zingdawng Sawl No, Hukdampa lalna gama chun,
 Lei lungkhamna leh buoina cheng tawh;
 Damlai lungngaih mei zing ta puona,
 Kap a kikhenna bei tana.

[V2]
 Lili pak leh lopina vak zam vel,
 Belam No leh a tatsa te lenna;
 Van khawtuol nuom leh Angelte,
 Muh ka nuom ngei ie.

[V3]
 2. Thilun van lopina tung masate haw chun,
 Pak na'n gihawih lopi a lem ui,
 Leia a len guol ten thil mah leu,
 Ngaiin nungsul hei ta puonau.

[V4]
 3. Zing tha puin van Jerusalem thak hawih ah,
 A leng tau ui van gam nuom achun,
 Lunglai ei kuoi hi a mel vak un
 Ka lungguk ah a dai thei puoi.

[V5]
 4. Chung thangvan gitna khel Lalpa chenna gamah,
 Ni vak leh thaumei ngai talo in,
 Zan thim lungngaihna cheng bei tana,
 Belam No chu a vak zing hi.</lyrics>
<title>Hukdampa Lalna Gam</title>
<hymn_number>185</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Zasiama</author>
</song>